        "subject": "LU-15420 snmp: avoid gcc-11 -Werror=sizeof-array-div warning",
        "message": "LU-15420 snmp: avoid gcc-11 -Werror=sizeof-array-div warning\n\nThis patch fixes the following warning:\n\nlustre-snmp.c: In function 'deinit_lustresnmp':\nlustre-snmp.c:715:64: error: expression does not compute\nthe number of elements in this array; element type is 'oid'\n{aka 'long unsigned int'}, not 'oid[7]'\n{aka 'long unsigned int[7]'} [-Werror=sizeof-array-div]\n  715 |                        sizeof(clusterFileSystems_variables_oid)/\n      |                                                                ^\n\nlustre-snmp.c:715:64: note: add parentheses around the second\n'sizeof' to silence this warning\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\n\nChange-Id: I5167044bb31b3b6f97223004298354917c6cc49c\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <yujian@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
